data.description: Welcome to your new home! This beautifully updated end-of-group townhome offers a perfect blend of style, comfort, and functionality. With an open floor plan, abundant natural light, and thoughtful features, this property is sure to impress. Here's a glimpse of what awaits you: This townhome features three bedrooms, providing ample space for a growing family or guests. The two full baths have been tastefully updated with modern fixtures and finishes. The home's open floor plan creates a welcoming and spacious atmosphere. Enjoy a seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas, perfect for both daily living and entertaining. Large Bay window allows natural light to flood the living spaces, creating a bright and airy ambiance. The property includes a large detached garage, providing convenient and secure parking. This versatile space can also be used for additional storage or as a workshop. The finished basement adds valuable living space to the home, offering flexibility for a family room, home office, or guest quarters. The property has been thoughtfully updated with modern amenities, ensuring a comfortable and stylish living experience. Conveniently located, this townhome is close to amenities, schools, and major transportation routes. Enjoy the benefits of a vibrant community while still having the privacy of an end-of-group property. This home is ready for you to move in and start creating memories. Experience the pride of ownership from the moment you step through the door. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautifully updated townhome your own. Schedule a showing today and envision the possibilities of living in this inviting and meticulously maintained property. Your new home awaits!
